{"tid":767303,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKUST]科大新生 2018 reg day 必讀！科大2018新生全攻略！","createTime":"2018-08-04T11:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T04:21:55.000Z","uid":77867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"662e6669012d5ea393d83168eddd2d30b60d1638","tid":767303,"uid":77867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"利申自己玩土木嘅 其他唔清楚不作評論<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post係教你如何開心過渡8/8，9/8嘅RegDay，同埋揀到心儀OCamp！<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好急，唔好俾人咁快水到<br />\n每當做Fm嘅你一落車，好多Soc就會即刻搶住你招呼你，好啲嘅會帶你去整學生證，跟住一路sell你OCamp，衰啲嘅某啲Soc會搵女夾住你色誘你去報，你唔報唔俾你走，呢個時候你唔好避，有禮貌啲講有冇單張睇下呀 最好拎多幾張 自己做比較 整完證再諗都唔遲呀。拉扯唔比你走就少不免，但係唔好咁快把持唔住就比錢，我做新生嘅時候就係咁。<br />\n不仿花少少時間睇下啲exco，有啲soc雖然人少少，但勝在有心，成個soc嘅人同exco都會好close。<br />\n<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\"> ](好多Soc你報完Ocamp俾埋錢係冇得退，所以考慮清楚)</span>[/size=5<br />\n<br />\n2. 提防聯盟式銷售<br />\n我唔想針對任何Soc，但呢招實在太狗所以想提提，有啲Soc為咗一條龍R到最多嘅組仔女，會「聯盟化」，一次過要你報4-5個Soc嘅OCamp，掠盡你水，最經典例子係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 「土木 經濟 四蛇 生化 社一」</span></span>聯盟，小弟就係咁先半推半就下玩左土木，就算你唔係想讀個個Major，佢都會水你入去，務求你肯俾錢，等你玩完OCamp見你唔係自己人就唔會再理你。其實，玩OCamp都係想識人，咁點解唔玩返個個Major嘅OCamp? 你可能話 車，個個Soc啲Exco都唔係個個Major，其實呢啲情況多數係Busi多發生，但so what? 組爸媽係架嘛 啲人脈仍然係架嘛 Fm們，First Year咋 識返自己圈子先啦<br />\n<br />\n3. Google<br />\nGoogle定個個Major嘅Soc嘅fb/ig/官網，睇下佢多唔多搞活動，又可以睇下佢地往年OCamp係搞成點，呢樣都係衡量值唔值得報個個OCamp，自己玩土木就覺得岩岩合格la，但唔係engine field 內做得最好嘅，可能係隔離飯香🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n最後，作為師兄嘅我又唔會叫你哋唔報OCamp，的確好嘅OCamp係對你First Year同ULife有極大幫助，而且風氣已變，宜家啲OCamp正氣咗健康咗架啦<br />\n<br />\n我建議報：最少一個Dept Soc OCamp(自己想讀嘅個個Major) + 額外一個興趣Soc OCamp，仲有錢先再報School Soc(ESU, BSU)，因為School Soc嘅圈子通常到Year 2就散，反而Dept Soc會好玩啲 不過都值得報嘅"},{"pid":"fe9644f0c9b3fb7b99c304c401be83558d6ecf5a","tid":767303,"uid":132968,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"First thing first: Just quit UST <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4c8b928fdb5afeeedbd0ee4813e620692089f0","tid":767303,"uid":132968,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/191736_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F191736_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7ef66d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKU: 21.9k<br />\nCUHK: 21.6k<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\nUST: 18k <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3c382414e9673764edb4b1dfab5b7025634b33","tid":767303,"uid":127922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e34caf1559a6623084bc7d7f062f50e802b2dc2","tid":767303,"uid":77867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c4c8b928fdb5afeeedbd0ee4813e620692089f0","tid":767303,"uid":132968,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/191736_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim